# Files excluded from the Docker build context.
#
# The `api/Dockerfile` is built with `context: .` (the repo root) so
# it can `COPY shared/`, `api/`, and `db/`. Anything not explicitly
# needed at build time — node_modules, build outputs, IDE state, VCS
# metadata, docs — should stay out of the context to keep the upload
# and build cache small.
#
# Reference: https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/builder/#dockerignore-file

# ─── Git / VCS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# ─── Node ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
.npm/
.pnpm-store/
.yarn/
.pnp.*

# ─── Build outputs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
dist/
build/
out/
.next/
.cache/
*.tsbuildinfo

# ─── Test output ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
coverage/
.nyc_output/
junit.xml

# ─── Netlify ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.netlify/
netlify/functions/proxy.zip

# ─── Editor / OS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ─── Env / secrets ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key

# ─── Local databases / caches ────────────────────────────────────────────
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
.agent_factory.db

# ─── Docker / compose state (this file too) ──────────────────────────────
docker-compose*.yml
.dockerignore
Dockerfile*

# ─── CI / docs / scripts (not needed in the image) ───────────────────────
.github/
docs/
README.md
*.md

# ─── Web frontend (built by Netlify, not by the API image) ───────────────
# We only need `web/package.json` for `npm ci` to resolve the workspace;
# the rest of the web tree is shipped to Netlify, not the API image.
web/node_modules/
web/dist/
web/src/
web/test/
web/public/
web/index.html
web/vite.config.ts
web/tsconfig*.json
web/vitest.config.ts
web/*.tsbuildinfo
web/coverage/

# ─── Netlify function (built by Netlify, not by the API image) ───────────
netlify/
